## GCLOUD

### Configuration

#### Create a new configuration
```bash
gcloud config configuration create <name>
```

#### Set properties for a configuration
```bash
gcloud config set project <project_id>
gcloud config set compute/zone <zone>
gcloud config set compute/region <region>
```

#### Activate a configuration
```bash
gcloud config configuration activate <name>
```

---

### Authentication & Setup

Before using any `gcloud` command you must authenticate and set a default project:

```bash
gcloud auth login
gcloud config set project <project_id>
```

#### Useful commands
```bash
gcloud init                      # Guide through initial settings
gcloud projects list             # List all projects
gcloud services list             # List enabled services
gcloud projects describe         # Describe a project
gcloud compute instances list    # List compute instances
```

