## Cloud Shell

- Fully managed, browser-based command-line environment directly in the Google Cloud Console
- Comes with Google Cloud SDK and `gcloud` pre-installed
- 5 GB of persistent storage
- Security patches managed by Google
- Includes a built-in Cloud Shell Editor (code editor)

### Persistent Storage Structure
~ (home directory)
├── tools/
├── projects/
└── bin/        ← Scripts here can be executed by name (included in default PATH)

### DevOps Use Cases
- Manage GCP resources without an external IP or SSH access

